      "name": "Pressure Rise Validation Against FDA Experimental Data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted pressure rise across the pump was compared against FDA-published experimental measurements at five flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute error was 8.3% across all conditions. Validation evidence was generated by the post-processing workflow for pressure outputs only.",
      "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "https://uofa.net/synth/activity/pressure-validation-run-vad"
